<http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/AssessmentMethod> rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/Authority
<http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/Authority> rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/BiodiversityAssessmentGuideline
<http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/BiodiversityAssessmentGuideline> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                rdfs:subClassOf <http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/Guidelines> .


###  http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/BiodiversityAssessmentMethod
<http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/BiodiversityAssessmentMethod> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                             rdfs:subClassOf <http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/AssessmentMethod> .


